The House of the Devil;;63;;85;;R;;Desperate to make some money so she can move into a new apartment, college student Samantha Hughes (Jocelin Donahue) takes a mysterious babysitting job. When she arrives at the house, Mr. Ulman (Tom Noonan) mentions a full lunar eclipse and explains there is no child, but that Samantha will be watching his mother instead. After exploring the sinister-seeming house, Samantha soon comes to realize that her employers are hiding a horrifying secret and have plans to use her, dead or alive.;;Horror;;Ti West;;2009;;Jocelin Donahue,Tom Noonan,Mary Woronov,Greta Gerwig,AJ Bowen,Dee Wallace,Heather Robb,John Speredakos,Mary B. McCann,Brenda Cooney;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_house_of_the_devil_2009